             <div class="twoj_tab_content" id="twoj_fragment1-1" style="overflow: hidden;">
              <br/>
              <h3>
               Mailing Lists
              </h3>
              There are two primary mailing lists for Uintah discussion.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              The
              <strong>
               uintah-users
              </strong>
              list is for any general question about using Uintah. We would like to encourage everyone to offer assistance to those that ask questions.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              The
              <strong>
               uintah-developer
              </strong>
              list is for those who are actively developing Uintah at either the framework level or at the component level.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              <strong>
               To sign up please visit:
              </strong>
              <br/>
              <ul>
               <li>
                <a href="https://gforge.sci.utah.edu/mailman/listinfo/uintah-users" target="_blank">
                 uintah-users
                </a>
               </li>
               <li>
                <a href="https://gforge.sci.utah.edu/mailman/listinfo/uintah-developer" target="_blank">
                 uintah-developer
                </a>
               </li>
               <li>
                <a href="https://gforge.sci.utah.edu/mailman/listinfo/uintah-commits" target="_blank">
                 uintah-commits
                </a>
               </li>
               <li>
                <a href="https://gforge.sci.utah.edu/gf/project/uintah/mailman/" target="_blank">
                 Archives
                </a>
                for the list are available.
               </li>
              </ul>
